totally work in progress ... not really meant for usage.
If you want to try anyways clone this repo, then open chrome, go to 

tools > extensions

expand developer mode and click 'Load unpacked extension' and select the directory with the repo.

In the options dialog add a hudson url without the api/json part, i.e.

http://hudson.hyperic.com/

click the 'jenkins' icon to get a list of jobs. Click on red/green square to expand list
